negative values move it up and to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the left."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Set the offset if the annotation view’s visual center point is somewhere other"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"than the logical center of the view. For example, the view may contain an image","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that depicts a downward-pointing pushpin or thumbtack, with the tip positioned"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"at the center-bottom of the view. In that case, you would set the offset’s "},{"code":"dx","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to zero and its "},{"code":"dy","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to half the height of the view."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/centeroffset"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","title":"MLNAnnotationView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/centerOffset":{"title":"centerOffset","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The offset, measured in points, at which to place the center of the view."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"centerOffset"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/centeroffset","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/centerOffset","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]}}}